## Commands

Per-runtime commands (build, dev, test, lint) live in
`.claude/runtimes/<name>.md` reference stamps. Per-cloud commands
(deploy, rollback) live in `.claude/clouds/<name>.md`. This section
is a short overview pointing at the right place.

{{ONE-LINE OVERVIEW: e.g. "Two runtimes: `api` (FastAPI on :8000)
and `web` (Vite on :5173). One cloud: `firebase-hosting` for the
web frontend. See `.claude/runtimes/` and `.claude/clouds/`."}}

| Top-level dispatch | Command |
|---|---|
| **List runtimes** | `ls .claude/runtimes/` |
| **List clouds** | `ls .claude/clouds/` |
| **Run a specific runtime** | See `commands.dev` in the runtime's stamp |
| **Test (verification gate)** | See `.claude/tests/` or each runtime's `commands.test` |

