## Deploy

Deploy targets and cloud surfaces are documented per-resource at
`.claude/clouds/<name>.md`. One file per cloud / deployment surface
(e.g. `firebase-hosting.md`, `azure-acr.md`, `azure-aks-prod.md`).
Run `ls .claude/clouds/` to see what this project has.

A short overview is fine here — what the project deploys at a high
level — but the per-surface details (auth, commands, gotchas) live
in `.claude/clouds/` so they're operable per-resource without scanning
this whole file.

